# Feedback Components

## Toast Notification
```jsx
<div role="alert" className="toast toast-success">
  <Icon name="check-circle" />
  <span>{MESSAGE}</span>
  <button aria-label="Close" onClick={dismiss}>×</button>
</div>
```
- **Variants**: Success, Error, Warning, Info
- **Position**: Top-right (desktop), Top (mobile)
- **Duration**: 3-5 seconds
- **Dismiss**: Auto-dismiss or manual close

## Modal Dialog
```jsx
<dialog open role="dialog" aria-labelledby="modal-title" aria-modal="true">
  <h2 id="modal-title">{TITLE}</h2>
  <p>{CONTENT}</p>
  <button onClick={confirm}>Confirm</button>
  <button onClick={cancel}>Cancel</button>
</dialog>
```
- **Backdrop**: Dark overlay (`rgba(0,0,0,0.5)`)
- **Focus trap**: Keep focus within modal
- **Escape key**: Close on `Esc`

## Progress Indicator
```jsx
<div role="progressbar" aria-valuenow={50} aria-valuemin={0} aria-valuemax={100}>
  <div style={{ width: '50%' }} />
</div>
```

## Loading Spinner
```jsx
<div role="status" aria-live="polite" aria-label="Loading">
  <svg className="spinner">...</svg>
</div>
```
